    "body": "@daejunpark I'm not sure that is fully correct, it would be only two of these scenarios because decimal assignment would not perform the division by `10^10`:\r\n\r\n`d = d * convert(i)` => `d = [d] * (i * 10^10)`\r\n`d = d / convert(i)` => `d = [d] / (i * 10^10)`\r\n`i = convert(d * convert(i))` => `i = ([d] * (i * 10^10) ) / 10^10` => `i = ([d] * i)`\r\n`i = convert(d / convert(i))` => `i = ([d] * 10^10) / (i * 10^10)` => `i = ([d] / i)`",
